Success Metrics & Accountability
- Weekly completion rate of planned tasks in `planning/semester-checklist.md`.
- Quality of test-first development practices (measured by test coverage and passing rates).
- Consistent note-taking and reflection in `notes/` directory.
- Meeting all assignment/lab deadlines with validation completed.
- Demonstrable OOP concept mastery through clean, well-structured code.

Priority Alignment Framework
- **High Priority**: Assignment deadlines, test-first development, OOP concept mastery.
- **Medium Priority**: Lab completion, comprehensive note-taking, code quality improvements.
- **Low Priority**: Advanced features, optimization beyond requirements, extensive documentation.
- **Avoid**: Gaming, non-academic video editing, relationship complications during study time.
